  <p>Effective Date: [Insert Date]</p>
  <p>Welcome to Script Sellers, the premier marketplace for creative and technical scripts. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website [Insert URL], use our mobile application, or engage with any of our related services (collectively, the "Services"). Please read this Privacy Policy carefully. If you do not agree with the terms of this policy, please do not access the site or use the Services.</p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We collect information that identifies, relates to, describes, references, is capable of being associated with, or could reasonably be linked, directly or indirectly, with a particular consumer or device ("personal information"). In particular, Script Sellers has collected the following categories of personal information from its consumers within the last twelve months:</p>
